# PR Conventions

- Do not add the issue ID to the PR title unless explicitly asked.
- When creating a PR, set the base branch to `develop` or `main` unless the user specifies otherwise.
- When opening a PR, assign it to `@stefanosala`.
- Open PR in Draft status, unless the user specifies otherwise.
